experience.description: Completed a full-year teaching internship within a high school mathematics department. Developed and executed daily lesson plans for Algebra I and Geometry, managed classroom environments of 25+ students, and participated in parent-teacher conferences and departmental curriculum mapping.

Supported lead teachers in the implementation of individualized education programs (IEPs) for students. Facilitated small group study sessions, provided one-on-one tutoring in core subject areas, and assisted with the grading of assignments and data entry.

Provided academic support to high school students in a community-based setting. Focused on improving literacy and numeracy skills while helping students prepare for standardized testing and college entrance exams.
